<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Sales Delegate Signup — sLab</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
    body { font-family:'Inter',sans-serif; background:#0a0a0a; color:#e5e5e5; min-height:100vh; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; padding:24px; }
    .signup-wrap { max-width:560px; width:100%; }
    .logo { font-size:24px; font-weight:600; color:#fff; text-align:center; margin-bottom:8px; } .logo span { color:#c9a848; }
    .subtitle { text-align:center; font-size:13px; color:#737373; margin-bottom:32px; }
    .card { background:#141414; border:1px solid #262626; border-radius:8px; padding:32px; }
    .card-title { font-size:18px; font-weight:600; color:#fff; margin-bottom:4px; }
    .card-desc { font-size:13px; color:#737373; margin-bottom:24px; line-height:1.6; }
    .form-row { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:16px; margin-bottom:16px; }
    .form-row.full { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .form-group { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:5px; }
    .form-group label { font-size:11px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-transform:uppercase; color:#737373; }
    .form-group input { background:#1a1a1a; border:1px solid #333; color:#e5e5e5; padding:10px 12px; border-radius:4px; font-family:'Inter',sans-serif; font-size:14px; outline:none; transition:border-color 0.15s; }
    .form-group input:focus { border-color:#c9a848; }
    .form-group input::placeholder { color:#525252; }
    .error { background:rgba(248,113,113,0.1); border:1px solid rgba(248,113,113,0.2); color:#f87171; padding:10px 14px; border-radius:4px; font-size:13px; margin-bottom:16px; }
    .commission-box { background:#1a1a1a; border:1px solid #262626; border-radius:6px; padding:16px; margin-bottom:20px; }
    .commission-box h3 { font-size:13px; font-weight:600; color:#c9a848; margin-bottom:10px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.8px; }
    .commission-row { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; padding:4px 0; font-size:13px; }
    .commission-row .label { color:#a3a3a3; } .commission-row .value { color:#fff; font-weight:600; }
    .disclaimer { background:#1a1a1a; border:1px solid #262626; border-radius:6px; padding:16px; margin-bottom:20px; max-height:180px; overflow-y:auto; }
    .disclaimer h3 { font-size:12px; font-weight:600; color:#c9a848; margin-bottom:8px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.8px; }
    .disclaimer p { font-size:12px; color:#a3a3a3; line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:8px; }
    .disclaimer p:last-child { margin-bottom:0; }
    .checkbox-row { display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:10px; margin-bottom:20px; }
    .checkbox-row input[type=checkbox] { width:18px; height:18px; margin-top:2px; accent-color:#c9a848; flex-shrink:0; }
    .checkbox-row label { font-size:13px; color:#a3a3a3; line-height:1.5; cursor:pointer; }
    .btn { width:100%; padding:12px; background:#c9a848; color:#0a0a0a; border:none; border-radius:4px; font-family:'Inter',sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-weight:600; cursor:pointer; transition:background 0.15s; }
    .btn:hover { background:#d4b85c; }
    .login-link { text-align:center; margin-top:16px; font-size:13px; color:#737373; }
    .login-link a { color:#c9a848; text-decoration:none; } .login-link a:hover { text-decoration:underline; }
    @media (max-width:520px) { .form-row { grid-template-columns:1fr; } .card { padding:20px; } }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="signup-wrap">
    <div class="logo"><span>s</span>Lab</div>
    <div class="subtitle">Sales Delegate Program</div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">Become a Sales Delegate</div>
      <div class="card-desc">Earn recurring commissions by referring businesses to the sLab platform. Sign up below to get started.</div>

      <% if (error) { %><div class="error"><%= error %></div><% } %>

      <div class="commission-box">
        <h3>Commission Structure</h3>
        <div class="commission-row"><span class="label">Year 1 (per account/month)</span><span class="value">$5.00</span></div>
        <div class="commission-row"><span class="label">Year 2 (per account/month)</span><span class="value">$2.50</span></div>
        <div class="commission-row"><span class="label">Year 3+ Lifetime (per account/month)</span><span class="value">$2.00</span></div>
      </div>

      <form method="POST" action="/delegates/signup">
        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>First Name *</label>
            <input type="text" name="firstName" value="<%= formData.firstName || '' %>" required placeholder="John">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Last Name *</label>
            <input type="text" name="lastName" value="<%= formData.lastName || '' %>" required placeholder="Doe">
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-row full">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Email *</label>
            <input type="email" name="email" value="<%= formData.email || '' %>" required placeholder="you@example.com">
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Phone</label>
            <input type="text" name="phone" value="<%= formData.phone || '' %>" placeholder="(555) 123-4567">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Address</label>
            <input type="text" name="address" value="<%= formData.address || '' %>" placeholder="123 Main St">
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>City</label>
            <input type="text" name="city" value="<%= formData.city || '' %>" placeholder="City">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>State</label>
            <input type="text" name="state" value="<%= formData.state || '' %>" placeholder="State">
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Zip</label>
            <input type="text" name="zip" value="<%= formData.zip || '' %>" placeholder="12345">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Password *</label>
            <input type="password" name="password" required placeholder="Min 12 chars, mixed case + number + symbol">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Confirm Password *</label>
            <input type="password" name="password_confirm" required placeholder="Re-enter password">
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="disclaimer">
          <h3>Tax & Payout Disclaimer</h3>
          <p>By signing up as a Sales Delegate, you acknowledge the following:</p>
          <p><strong>Tax Responsibility:</strong> You are an independent contractor, not an employee. You are solely responsible for reporting all commission income to the appropriate tax authorities. sLab will issue a 1099 form (or equivalent) for annual earnings exceeding $600.</p>
          <p><strong>Tax Information Required:</strong> You must provide valid tax information (W-9 or equivalent) before receiving your first payout. Failure to provide tax documentation will result in payout holds.</p>
          <p><strong>Contact & Address:</strong> You are responsible for keeping your mailing address, email, and phone number current. Outdated contact information may delay payouts or tax documents.</p>
          <p><strong>Payout Schedule:</strong> Commissions are calculated monthly and paid according to the current payout schedule. sLab reserves the right to modify commission rates for new signups with 30 days notice. Existing account commissions are honored at the rate in effect at time of signup.</p>
          <p><strong>Account Eligibility:</strong> Commission is earned only on active, paying tenant accounts. Suspended, cancelled, or free/preview accounts do not generate commissions.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="checkbox-row">
          <input type="checkbox" name="agreedDisclaimer" id="disclaimer" value="yes">
          <label for="disclaimer">I have read and agree to the Tax & Payout Disclaimer above. I understand I must provide tax information before receiving my first payment.</label>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="btn">Create Delegate Account</button>
      </form>

      <div class="login-link">Already have an account? <a href="/delegates/login">Log in</a></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
